  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of present study was to evaluate the clinical course after emergency ventral hernia
      repair in terms of 30-day-readmission, -reoperation and -mortality and to identify risk
      factors for emergency repair.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      All incisional, umbilical and epigastric hernias registered in the Danish Ventral Hernia
      Database
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
